Invocation Name: what fruits are seasonal
des: Use this skill to find out what fruits are in season right now! With this, you can go to the grocery store knowing right away which ones will be the freshest, ripest fruit ready to eat. No more sour peaches or bland oranges, just use this skill and get that fruit!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
